**PRIVACY POLICY**

Tambola Cheat App is an Android app provided by Aditya Gupta. This service is offered at no cost and is intended for responsible and ethical use.

This page explains how we handle data and information in this app, and what we do with the data collected from users.

By using our service, you agree to the terms outlined in this Privacy Policy. Any personal information collected is used to enhance the service and is treated with utmost confidentiality. We do not share or misuse your data in any way.

**Information Collection and Use**

While using our Service, we may request certain information for a better user experience. However, the information provided is not collected in any way and is retained on your device.

The app may utilize third-party services that collect data to improve user identification.

**Log Data**

Please note that when you use our Service, in the event of an app error, we may collect Log Data through third-party products. This data can include your device's Internet Protocol (“IP”) address, device name, operating system version, app configuration, usage time, and other statistics.

**Cookies**

Our Service does not use "cookies" explicitly. Nonetheless, the app may contain third-party code and libraries that utilize “cookies” for data collection and service enhancement. You have the choice to accept or decline these cookies.

**Service Providers**

We may engage third-party companies and individuals for various purposes related to the Service. These entities may have access to your Personal Information only to execute the tasks assigned to them on our behalf, with strict obligations not to use or disclose this data for any other purposes.

**Security**

Your trust is invaluable to us, and we employ industry-standard methods to protect your Personal Information. However, it's important to understand that no data transmission over the internet or electronic storage method is entirely secure. We cannot guarantee absolute security.

**Links to Other Sites**

Our Service may include links to external sites. If you click on a third-party link, you will be directed to that site. These external sites are not operated or managed by us, and we recommend reviewing their Privacy Policies. We have no control over or responsibility for the content, privacy policies, or practices of these third-party sites.

**User Responsibility**

Users of this Service are solely responsible for their actions and usage. The app is intended for ethical and legitimate purposes only.

**Children’s Privacy**

Our Services are not intended for users under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personally identifiable information from children under 13. If you believe that your child has provided us with personal information, please contact us to take necessary actions.

**Changes to This Privacy Policy**

We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. We recommend reviewing this page periodically for any changes. We will notify users of any changes by posting the revised Privacy Policy on this page.

This Privacy Policy is effective as of [Effective Date].

